OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLGBT military ban: Veterans
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto share impact of rules in
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Freview, 20 years on        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, LGBT veterans have cautiously welcomed 
OL,6, a review into the impact of a ban on   
OL,7, them serving in the military, which has
OL,8, been launched more than 20 years after 
OL,9, the law was changed.                   
OL,11,FUntil 2000 it was illegal to be gay in 
OL,12,Fthe British military - a rule that's   
OL,13,Fthought to have affected about 5,000   
OL,14,Fpeople in the armed forces.            
OL,16,FThe review will look at what could be  
OL,17,Fdone now to help support those people. 
OL,19,FCampaigners hope the review's outcome  
OL,20,Fwill entitle them to compensation.     
